snippet.title: BAROQUE: Become a Meta-Being
snippet.description:
BAROQUE ～ふと目を覚ますと異形になっていた～
■App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1598463932
■Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.sting.baroquew

新作アプリが、Android・iOSにて無料で遊べます。
タップして進むだけの超簡単ハイパーカジュアルゲーム、1000メートルを目指せ‼

BAROQUE: Become a Meta-Being
You can play the new app for free on Android or iOS.
It's a super easy casual game that you could just tap the screen to proceed.
Can you exceed 1000 meters!?
#iPhone
#Android
